A vintage 1950s-style illustration of a determined office worker in rolled-up sleeves operating an enormous brass and copper steampunk machine with multiple spinning gears, pistons, and vacuum tubes. The machine has a large funnel at the top where glowing clouds pour in, while at the bottom, neatly organized filing cabinet drawers automatically fill with perfectly stacked papers. The scene has warm sepia and amber tones with dramatic shadows, reminiscent of mid-century industrial posters. Steam wisps curl around the machinery as indicator dials and pressure gauges display various readings. The worker pulls a large lever with confidence while monitoring the automated archival process.
